  "3183230": {
    "name": "Dream Strikers",
    "steam_appid": 3183230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/6b26bc9e5a448988ada96c3bea29c49e.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/6b26bc9e5a448988ada96c3bea29c49e.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/314f469a02c9e00a413db20817671764.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦魇猎人》是一款轻松上手的 3D 格斗动作游戏，拥有高机动战斗系统与炫酷的招式特效。玩家可以自由选择势力，以赛博奇幻风的战场为舞台，在连段与闪避交织的战斗中施展华丽技能，感受拳拳到肉的极致打击感。无论是单人挑战还是双人对战，都能享受到节奏紧凑且上手容易的畅快格斗体验！每一场对决，都是一场信念与执念的碰撞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/5581a1c5e5ef441e955c9d1b31a9c650.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/5581a1c5e5ef441e955c9d1b31a9c650.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/1aedd72cb33defb6a1a60016c5c931c8.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有惊艳的视觉表现，无论是角色的动态表情、战斗中的光影特效，还是每一张场景的细节刻画，都力求真实震撼。通过精细的图像处理技术，游戏呈现出前所未有的临场感，让每一场战斗都成为一场视觉盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/98ca14a75844d1b59fa4b322fcd8ed16.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/98ca14a75844d1b59fa4b322fcd8ed16.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/3b1dc2071117feab51fcfe8790bbfbd4.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同于以往的格斗游戏，采用双镜头系统，自动在 2D / 3D 视角之间切换，在保留攻击自由度的同时，强化动作表现力与战斗节奏感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/a7c5a107be06640443f41498e234e2a3.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/a7c5a107be06640443f41498e234e2a3.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/c01504751ddc8db31940a54f3993e5c8.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关键时刻释放潜能，施展奥义终结技，一击定胜负。爆发怒气之力，以压倒性的攻势终结对手，展现华丽且致命的一击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/d1789e174ab69160451e76a7c5905bc8.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/d1789e174ab69160451e76a7c5905bc8.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/737ad429636b5aaaf46c14d5ecbaddae.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的战斗系统允许玩家根据战况自由组合攻击技能，创造属于自己的战斗风格。无论是新手还是老玩家，都可以轻松上手，并在战斗中挖掘更多可能性。游戏中的每位角色都有独特的技能与战斗风格，让你在对战中体验到无限自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/7673b64ee17a9d2c7e47f6cbe968df25.poster.avif?t=1762012417\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/7673b64ee17a9d2c7e47f6cbe968df25.webm?t=1762012417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183230/extras/51a137b293bc9a7d68ebf83095263b22.avif?t=1762012417\" width=1232 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有多位风格迥异的角色，每一位都有独特的背景故事与作战方式。无论你选择谁，都将进入一个充满挑战与情感的世界。随着剧情推进，玩家将逐步揭开隐藏在梦魇背后的真相，与深渊中的敌人展开生死对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持本地与好友联机双人对战，可与朋友实时对抗。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供单人街机模式，挑战特制 AI 与多重关卡。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前开放 4 位独具特色的可选角色。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有 8 张风格各异的梦境战斗场景，包含天空、遗迹、都市等主题。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场对决皆可体验高机动战斗与华丽终结技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
